Goddess of the moon and hunt.<br>
Protectress of women and children during childbirth. Guardian of all the worlds Harbors and Roads.<br>
My domain are all the worlds mountains.<br>
I have the power to send plagues to mortal lands.<br>
<br>
Daughter of Zeus and Leto, the Goddess of Asia Minor.<br>
Twin sister to Apollo, the Golden God. I am known as the Silver Goddess. My archery exceeds all. I am known to hunt with my mother, brother and sometimes accompionied by Orion, a giant hunter.<br>
<br>
My largest temple sits in Ephesus.<br>
My sacred candle colors are silver and white.<br>
A patron goddess of witches.<br>
I am quick to protect wildlife and animals, as well as humans who appeal to me for help,espcially women who are raped or victumized by men.<br>
<br>
I hold second council chair upon Olympus.<br>
<br>
<br>
