The Amazonian Moon Goddess, she was worshiped at Ephesus, her entire torso covered with nurturing breasts. <br>
Artemis' bow is symbolic of both the crescent Moon as well as of inner self-esteem, of an exquisitely tuned inner tension. <br>
  <br>
